<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4671506>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 5. Aulodrilus pluriseta (Piguet) from Lake Kasumigaura, Japan (A–G) and from Estonia (H and I). A, dorsal hair chaeta in an anterior segment; B, dorsal crotchet in IV; C, dorsal crotchet in a posterior segment; D, ventral chaeta in VIII; E and F, distal ends of dorsal crotchets; G, ventral view of distal end of ventral chaeta in anterior segment; H, ventral view of anterior segments showing locations of alimentary canal and genital organs; I, ventral view of genital segments. H and I are from one whole-mounted specimen." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4671506/files/figure.png" .

